# 1. THE NUCLEAR OPTION: Ignore literally everything in the folder
*

# 2. ALLOW DIRECTORIES: Git must be allowed to see folders, or it can't look inside them
!*/

# 3. THE WHITELIST: Only allow these specific file extensions

# Git files
!.gitignore

# Hardware Source Code
!*.vhd
!*.vhdl
!*.v
!*.sv

# Critical Quartus Project Files
!*.qpf
!*.qsf

# Timing Constraints & System Design
!*.sdc
!*.qsys

# Quartus Archives (Included as requested)
!*.qar
